{"tid":662133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川大地震死亡學童家長: 512感恩日?是否應該感恩豆腐渣工程","createTime":"2018-05-12T07:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T07:23:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0756e7d27c4b77c89018d08042c05d4be51057cf","tid":662133,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"四川汶川地震十周年，在重災區北川，倒塌造成大量傷亡的北川中學遺址，有數十名死亡學童的家長在監視下進行祭祀。<br />\n<br />\n有家長指堅持為要為兒子討回公道，但被人阻止上訪。有家長則不滿政府將512定為「感恩日」，認為是挖開家屬的傷口，反問是否應該感恩豆腐渣工程。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396003-20180512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396003-20180512.htm&d=JjlPAKBfLcjFdlmPxKK6DAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8749a742\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396003-20180512.htm&h=f4a1617c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396003-20180512.htm</a>"}]}